Description: JSON config distribution service with rule-based patching
 config-weaver distributes JSON configuration from an encrypted base
 file and applies optional patch rules based on user, client agent,
 and version.
 .
 It provides both a CLI and a FastAPI service, and is intended for
 simple GET-only clients and reverse-proxy deployments.
